import { GridItem, Heading } from '@chakra-ui/layout'
import React from 'react'

import AspectCard from './AspectCard'
function Homepage() {

    <GridItem colSpan={3}>
      <Heading> The Classical Maya </Heading>
      <Stack direction='row'>
        <AspectCard />
        <AspectCard />
      </Stack>
    </GridItem>
  )
}

export default Homepage
